09462730398666", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12410209_1139850796101484_7494319160986435584_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=9SdFaCt-5XAQ7kNvgFR9Due&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB5d8d-oTcTvwm6xdj2TYG5YYHs7oHLZstMzyjszcazCw&oe=67407395"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "205553077385065", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12680519_669995543176343_2050891396881055744_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VTBjSH53eY4Q7kNvgFY8EIZ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCC8VJ0L-b5sz_foinXXTQ_WuRf2WF2kZ-LvwgeDmnJiw&oe=674069A2"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "theViewer", "keywords": ["360", "Panorama", "Picture", "Archviz", "Architecture"], "long_description": "Easiest way to create and enjoy full VR Tours on your smartphone. \nSimply log on our platform ( theViewer.co), create a VR Tour by linking your 360\u00b0 images and view in your gallery or just copy the files to your Download folder on your phone . \n\nNo matter if you are an architect or an amateur photographer, it takes 3 quick steps to create a VR tour on theViewer: \n\nStep 1: Export spherical render images of your design or take real 360\u00b0 pictures \n\nStep 2: Use our online platform and place warp points that let you navigate through multiple panoramas \n\nStep 3: View through your PC on our online platform, embed in your site, post direct links on social networks such as Facebook, or view on your VR device via our app.", "short_description": "Easiest way to create and enjoy full VR Tours on your smartphone. \n\nSimply log on our platform ( theViewer.co), create a VR Tour by linking your 360\u00b0 images and view in your gallery or just copy the files to your Download folder on your phone. \n\nNo matter if you are an architect or an amateur photographer, it takes only few steps to create a VR Tour !"}]}, "developer_name": null, "d